import scarlet from '../images/scarlet.PNG' import green from '../images/green.PNG' import mustard from '../images/mustard.PNG' import white from '../images/white.PNG' import plum from '../images/plum.PNG' import peacock from '../images/peacock.PNG' import {useEffect} from 'react' import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import '../styles/character.css' import io from 'socket.io-client' const socket = io.connect('http://localhost:4000'); export default function Character(){ const navigate = useNavigate(); function gameBoard(){ navigate('/board'); } function selected(character){ if(document.getElementById(character).textContent === "Select"){ document.getElementById(character).textContent = "Selected"; socket.emit("send_message", {"message": [character, 'true']}); }else{ document.getElementById(character).textContent = "Select"; socket.emit("send_message", {"message": [character, 'false']}); } } useEffect(() => { socket.on("receive_message", (data) => { if (data.message[1] === 'true'){ document.getElementById(data.message[0]).textContent = "Selected"; }else{ document.getElementById(data.message[0]).textContent = "Select"; } }); }, []); return(
